data.description: 4BR, 2.5BA. Comfort and functionality! Boasting a main-level bedroom for added convenience, this home offers a versatile and open layout. Completely updated HVAC, newer appliances, and custom built-ins in the main bedroom closet. The  fenced backyard and garage provide both security and convenience.   The heart of the home features an eat-in kitchen with an additional breakfast bar, ideal for casual dining or entertaining. The large unfinished basement presents endless possibilities for expansion, hobbies, and storage.  Enjoy exclusive access to 2 private beaches, a tranquil lake, and inviting community areas.  Close proximity to shopping and amenities.  (VIDEO TOUR UPLOADED)
